Text: See diagram for specific set-up locations.
Please set out the air purifiers (one in the front, one in the back). Opening turn them on to level 3, closing turn them off and unplug.
Opening please unplug bug lights & hang them up in the chair closet. Closing, plug them back in.
Client should arrive to begin setting up the room.
Event should end. Load out will begin.
Load out should be complete. Put away any AV that was used. Check for any lost and
found items (note in closing & slack Bri). Cleaning: Remove trash from PCL,
